{"tid":1933940,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人要離開武漢，需要幾長時間？","createTime":"2020-03-19T15:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T15:39:01.000Z","uid":278351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"42af2637c0cea1f9bcb79a453de7f8b2f161229c","tid":1933940,"uid":278351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"唔知道幾時開始，<br />\n武漢肺炎爆發，<br />\n聽連登仔講呢個世界上芝麻人無一個係蘑菇的，<br />\n佢哋只係韭菜，<br />\n成熟咗就俾人收割，<br />\n呢種菜一生只可以言論自由一次，<br />\n而嗰一次就係佢死亡嘅時候。<br />\n<br />\n我一直以為芝麻有共產黨已經夠低質，<br />\n直到連英國、北韓甚至日本<br />\n幾乎全世界嘅政府都放棄佢哋嘅國民。<br />\n我開始懷疑，<br />\n喺呢個世界上，<br />\n仲有冇人係磨菇㗎？"},{"pid":"8e88fa959d26244d0250acdc3796346e480ecec7","tid":1933940,"uid":278351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:06:56.000Z","msg":"我曾經問自己，<br />\n民主國家同共產國家係咪唔一樣，<br />\n原來喺龐大嘅老年人口面前，<br />\n所有國家都一樣。"},{"pid":"1f413879b6d23a2e078543f21918753605d7dd95","tid":1933940,"uid":5103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:09:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">[本土youtube戰線][黃頁］面對偷圖狗，我哋創作愈做愈灰心（認真post)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1932944\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1932944</a><br />\n<br />\n我地已經比人抄到灰哂機<br />\n想請巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8836d4b415cf6e38a192b6ab33bb07861eee6f","tid":1933940,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:38:43.000Z","msg":"想唔想外國疫症恐慌期間收到香港嘅鼓勵！<br />\n睇呢度：<br />\n我想做多次全球宣傳 正中國肺炎視聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1930664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1930664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8559a9145c6a5f59e5c922a581b80685204df0b9","tid":1933940,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:39:01.000Z","msg":"如果有多一個豬咀<br />\n你會唔會同我一齊走？"}]}